name: The Wonderful World of Mickey Mouse
original_name: The Wonderful World of Mickey Mouse
overview: It's nothing but fun and excitement for Mickey and his best pals – Minnie, Donald, Daisy, Goofy and Pluto - as they embark on their greatest adventures yet, navigating the curveballs of a wild and zany world where the magic of Disney makes the impossible possible.

episodes.name: Cheese Wranglers
episodes.overview: Mickey Mouse has his work cut out for him as he tries to wrangle a prized herd, but Peg-Leg Pete gets in the way.

episodes.name: House of Tomorrow
episodes.overview: Mickey, Donald, and Goofy experience tomorrow's tech after sneaking into Von Drake's latest invention.

episodes.name: Hard to Swallow
episodes.overview: Mickey experiences frustration and trouble when he attempts to get Pluto to swallow a simple little pill.

episodes.name: School of Fish
episodes.overview: Mickey Mouse has a difficult time trying to let Gubbles go on his first day of school and must find a way to cope.

episodes.name: Keep on Rollin'
episodes.overview: Mickey Mouse and his friends' roller disco night is thrown into jeopardy by Peg-Leg Pete and his gang.

episodes.name: The Big Good Wolf
episodes.overview: Micky Mouse has his work cut out for him when he attempts to turn the Big Bad Wolf into a better person.

episodes.name: The Brave Little Squire
episodes.overview: Mickey dreams of being a knight but discovers his new boss' heroic reputation is a fairytale.

episodes.name: An Ordinary Date
episodes.overview: Mickey and Minnie are hard at work trying to make their ordinary dinner date into something extraordinary.

episodes.name: Supermarket Scramble
episodes.overview: Mickey and his friends’ plans for a barbeque get sidetracked after a quick trip to the supermarket turns into an odyssey.

episodes.name: Just the Four of Us
episodes.overview: Donald and Daisy's little lie becomes a big problem when they try to get out of a group date.

episodes.name: Houseghosts
episodes.overview: When several ghosts are left without a home to haunt, Mickey invites them to stay, but they prove to be the worst houseguests.

episodes.name: The Enchanting Hut
episodes.overview: Mickey and Minnie struggle to build a shelter after a raging storm threatens to destroy their idyllic island paradise.

episodes.name: Duet for Two
episodes.overview: Mickey and Minnie seek to make everyone happy by playing an adorable duet.

episodes.name: Birdwatching
episodes.overview: When Minnie’s quest to photograph an elusive bird places Mickey in danger, she must venture to save him before the bird’s motherly instincts seal his doom.

episodes.name: Bellboys
episodes.overview: Bellboys Mickey, Donald, and Goofy seek to revive a rundown hotel’s future after being put in charge for the night.

episodes.name: I Heart Mickey
episodes.overview: When Minnie misplaces Mickey’s gift of love, she must defeat a lover’s lane to retrieve it.

episodes.name: Untold Treasures
episodes.overview: Crewmates Mickey and Minnie seek to find a buried treasure before Peg-Leg Pete uses it to become the most powerful pirate on the seven seas.

episodes.name: Disappearing Act
episodes.overview: Mickey scrambles to rescue Minnie after accidentally making her disappear with a magic wand.

episodes.name: Once Upon an Apple
episodes.overview: Mickey’s quest to make everyone smile hits a snag when he meets a Wicked Witch bent on delivering poison apples to the fairest one in the land.

episodes.name: Game Night
episodes.overview: Mickey’s friends are placed in jeopardy after he attempts to spice up their weekly game night.
